Waiting for Happiness (cyangwa: '''''Heremakono''''' ) ni filime y'ikinamico yo muri [[Moritaniya|Mauritania]]  yakozwe muri 2002 yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Abderrahmane Sissako <ref>Waiting for Happiness - Rotten Tomatoes <nowiki>https://www.rottentomatoes.com</nowiki> › waiting_for_happine...</ref>. abakinnyi nyamukuru ni umunyeshuri, wagarutse iwabo i Nouadhibou, umutoza w’umwana, hamwe n’abagore baho<ref>Waiting for Happiness - Celluloid Dreams <nowiki>https://www.celluloid-dreams.com</nowiki> › waiting-for-happin...</ref>. Iyi filime irangwa nuruhererekane rwerekana ubuzima bwa buri munsi bw'abantu bavugwa mu mico yabo yihariye y’umuco nyafurika n’abarabu, mu gihe hari ibyo bakura muri tropes yigihe cya Tayeb Saleh cyo kwimukira mu majyaruguru ( موسم الهجرة إلى الشمال )<ref>Waiting for Happiness | Film Review | Spirituality & Practice <nowiki>https://www.spiritualityandpractice.com</nowiki> › reviews › view</ref>. Abareba bagomba kwisobanurira ibyabaye nta ruhare runini rw'abavuga cyangwa umugambi<ref>Waiting for happiness (Film, 2002) [WorldCat.org] <nowiki>https://www.worldcat.org</nowiki> › waiting-for-happiness › oclc</ref>, , ibyinshi bikaba bigarukwaho mubindi bikorwa muri opus ya Abderrahmane Sissako, harimo amashusho kuri saro yogosha hamwe nicyumba cyamafoto, nacyo kiboneka muri ''La Vie Sur Terre'' <ref>Film screening of Waiting for Happiness (Heremakono, 2002 ... <nowiki>https://www.rochester.edu</nowiki> › news › show</ref> . Iyi filime irerekana ibihe bisanzwe bya Mauritania byubwiza, urugamba, kwitandukanya, no gusetsa, bibaho mumatsinda atandukanijwe muburyo butandukanye<ref>Waiting For Happiness (En Attendandt le bonheure ... <nowiki>https://cineuropa.org</nowiki> › film</ref>, nkabagore ba Bidhan banywa icyayi no gusebanya, abimukira bo muri Afrika yuburengerazuba banyura muri Mauritania kugirango bagere i Burayi <ref>Waiting for Happiness - Celluloid Dreams <nowiki>https://www.celluloid-dreams.com</nowiki> › waiting-for-happin...</ref>. Umusore w'intwari wagarutse akorana naya matsinda yose nk'umuntu wo hanze, mugihe arwana no kwibuka ndetse nimvugo ye y'icyarabu ya Hassaniya, ariko ahitamo ahubwo [[igifaransa]] <ref>french films > Waiting for Happiness - France in London <nowiki>http://www.franceinlondon.com</nowiki> › en-French-films-530-...</ref>. . Waiting for Happiness yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2002 mu gice cya Un Certain Regard <ref>Waiting For Happiness | Reviews | guardian.co.uk Film <nowiki>https://www.theguardian.com</nowiki> › film › Observer_review</ref>. 

